text: Novyye Karashidy () is a rural locality (a village) in Cherkassky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 97 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 41 km from Ufa, 9 km from Cherkassy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Novyye Karashidy
